    # game/areas/howlersdell3othernpcs.rpy:317
    old "He raises his eyebrow. “I can tell you’ve been looking for them for quite some time. Everyone brings here what they have in abundance, en I either sell it to travelers, or divide it among the workers, builders, artisans. These things here are ne {i}mine{/i},” he runs his eyes over the crates and barrels, “but I can show you our wares, if you want. But if you can ne afford something, I’m ne going to haggle. I need to explain maself for every deal I make, or {color=#f6d6bd}Thais{/color} will laugh at me all the way to the pyre.” "
