    # game/areas/howlersdell3othernpcs.rpy:343
    old "You hear {color=#f6d6bd}Akakios’{/color} voice. “Here to see me? Just a minute, I usually start a bit later.” The man walks by you and goes behind the counter, where he starts to unpack and inspect his wares. “Speak whilst I’m young.” "
