    # game/areas/howlersdell3othernpcs.rpy:414
    old "“I’ll ask at {color=#f6d6bd}Bion’s{/color}, her wife had some of those.” After a few minutes, he brings you a clay pot with a plant not larger than your hand. It has a single flower, and a couple of healthy leaves. “Back in spring, {color=#f6d6bd}Asterion{/color} asked us to grow them, but he’s nae longer around, that little stinker. Eva their presence annoys me now. Three dragons en I’ll give you what’s above the ground. Maybe it will grow again.” \n\nYou ask him what he knows about it. He picks it up to look at it closely, as if it’s his first time seeing it. “Well, the forest speaker from the southern cave told me ‘tis a herb for potions. {i}Snake bait{/i}, he said. I think it lures serpents? I’m ne sure. But ‘tis pleasant in taste, I think?” "
