    # game/areas/howlersdell3othernpcs.rpy:3677
    old "You enter the building site, which has changed quite a bit since the last day of your visit. {color=#f6d6bd}Elpis{/color} is standing in the middle of the yard, surrounded by her companions, yet she needs a few breaths to collect her thoughts. \n\n“I am... {i}We{/i} are glad to see you, roadwarden,” her eyes make you think of a sky just after a heavy rain. “The forest speaker had put us into shame, en we’ve discussed his words en deeds.” Her voice is slow, but you catch its hesitation. “We’re grateful that the village of {color=#f6d6bd}Old Págos{/color} will share the next summer with us. The lack of the Seed will be a burden... But it will bring us to brighter days.” "
