    # game/areas/howlersdell3othernpcs.rpy:3912
    old "[custom1]You approach the building site. The stone foundations are finished, and the timber frame is jointed together with a set of intriguing cuts, like a large toy. One day, their walls will be whitewashed with limestone and turned into a prestigious shelter, unlike the houses made of logs and boards. \n\nThe other buildings are surrounded by grass, flowers, and herbs. The turmoil of village life is drowned out by the sound of the creek, but the knocking of a hammer shatters this tranquility. {color=#f6d6bd}The builders{/color} give you curious looks from above the log they’re cutting. "
