    # game/areas/howlersdell3othernpcs.rpy:3956
    old "She’s standing like a statue. “We’re far from this feeling. Every change is a threat, en {i}strangers{/i} bring them more than forest fires.” She opens her eyes and for a moment they are shinier, brighter, but also hostile. “{i}Your{/i} people would see your words as kind, but you are, en will be, an outsider. We’ll listen, but you’ll ne change us.” "
