    # game/areas/howlersdell3othernpcs.rpy:3965
    old "Her lips form a gentle smile. “En so are we. If you’re ne like the other cityfolk en you’re willing to {i}be{/i}, rather than {i}change{/i},” she pauses and opens her eyes, which are now as shiny as a midday sky. “we’re {i}curious{/i} to learn of the thoughts you bring.” "
