    # game/areas/howlersdell3othernpcs.rpy:5861
    old "“Sounds like a worker! But make sure he will ne oppose the marriage rites! His village follows The Wright, I need his word he’ll leave his spirit behind him. If he agrees,” her teeth are yellowish, but healthy, “he can come in fall, we’ll see how we get along!” "
