    # game/areas/howlersdell3othernpcs.rpy:6035
    old "“Have you ne heard of {color=#f6d6bd}The Tribe of The Green Mountain{/color}? Once as strong as our very own {color=#f6d6bd}Howler’s{/color}, got squashed by the city corsairs, pushed all the way to the distant East. Someone younger surely knows the way,” he looks around, as if an ancient pagan village could be hiding just behind the corner. “But you will ne be let in without a fine gift. Something they lack, no wonder. A sharp blade, bags of spices.” \n\nHe notices an angry look from {color=#f6d6bd}the innkeeper{/color}. “Aye, aye. {i}Do ne talk about The Green Mountain{/i},” in his screech you recognize {color=#f6d6bd}Thais’{/color} discipline. “I do ne care,” he raises his voice, but then has to clear his throat. "
